<!-- <b>General tips</b> -->
<b>注意事项</b>
<br /><br />
<!-- - avoid filenames with special characters or spaces in it<br /> -->
<!-- - use always only one camera for rendering<br /> -->
<!-- - when rendering single images, the image height has to be a multiple of 4 (low), 8 (medium) or 16 (high resolution)<br /> -->
<!-- - manage your files in a project (a project directory with all files belonging to it)<br /> -->
<!-- - when working with additional files like textures, always choose the path out of your project directory (relative instead of absolute)<br />  -->
<!-- - pack the scene file and all other needed files into one archive without any subdirectories<br /> -->
<!-- - you can use the following archive types: rar, zip, tgz, tbz2 (DO NOT use tar.gz or tar.bz2)<br /> -->
<!-- - upload the archive file in the form<br /> -->
- 文件名中要避免出现特殊字符或空格<br />
- 一个渲染任务只允许指定一台摄像机<br /> 
- 单帧渲染时，像素是4倍(低)、8倍(中)或16倍(高清晰度)<br />
