<a name="cinema4d"></a>
<b>使用Cinema4D进行渲染</b>
<br /><br />

<!-- - DO NOT use any advanced rendering functions like Global Illumination, Caustics, Ambient Occlusion, Effects (we don't have support for it yet)<br />
- open your scene<br />
- at 'Render Settings' -> 'Save' enable 'Save Image' and add a name with no path into the textbox<br />
- do not use a video format when rendering animations because it's far better to have all frames as single images (create a video out of them later)<br />
- at 'Options' enable 'Log File' to be able to see some more output in the logfiles<br />
- to get all material paths right, save your scene into a new directory via 'File' -> 'Save Project...'<br />
- pack the contents of that directory and upload the archive<br /><br /> -->
 
- 目前不支持全局光，焦散，環境光，特效等高级渲染函数<br />
- 打开场景<br />
- 在'Render Settings' -> 'Save'中勾选'Save Image'并在文本框中添加不带路径的文件名<br />
- 不要使用视频格式进行动画渲染，因为这要比将所有帧渲成单张图片好的多(渲染完成后创建视频)<br />
- 在'Options'中勾选'Log File'以便在日志文件中看到更多的细节<br />
- 通过'File' -> 'Save Project...'将场景文件保存到一个新的目录中来获得正确的材质路径<br />
- 压缩那个目录并上传<br /><br />



 
